-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TRAINING DATA ATTRIBUTION

This adapter was trained using the MedMCQA dataset (pediatric subjects subset),
an openly available medical question answering dataset derived from AIIMS and
NEET-PG medical entrance examinations.

    Dataset: MedMCQA
    Source: https://medmcqa.github.io
    License: MIT License

